              "fromCapturePath": "$.staleDigestRegister.variables.translations"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "notes": "Live Admin GraphQL 2026-04 capture creates one disposable product, ensures French is enabled, reads the product title digest, captures correct-digest success, fabricated-digest INVALID_TRANSLATABLE_CONTENT, updates the product title, captures stale-digest INVALID_TRANSLATABLE_CONTENT, then deletes the product and restores the locale only when the script enabled it."
